post.body:
Read it and weep..😱😀  This post disappeared so I'm re-posting it. Fortunately editing our previous post is one of the many, many excellent features of #Zeronet. Thanks @nofish

Ive been experimenting with different ways of posting content on the OPEN! internet. Content and free speech that some may find objectionable, and in some places even illegal. Like so-called pornographic or nsfw content.

Let me be perfectly clear. My experiments have absolutely nothing to do with validating or agreeing with these labels. These labels are mostly just an attempt to censor content and free speech by proxy. They are an attempt to steal power they don't rightfully deserve. Fuck! Them. :)

Res ipsa loquitur "The thing speaks for itself". As I previously said, I have decided to limit any post that may be interpreted as #nsfw to this, or other individual identities. I absolutely WILL NOT! label my post as anything other than what I chose to post them as. I don't believe in, nor will I support any form or kind of censorship on the OPEN! internet. The Harm! far outweighs the good.

I have learned that #Zeronet is enormously powerful at giving individual Users control over the content they choose to see or post. There is absolutely NO! excuse for third\turd party censorship proxies.

Individual Users can mute, un-mute other individual Users. Follow, un-follow individual Users. Images don't display by default, and can be deleted or re-displayed at will. Users can have different identities that they only use for work etc.. You get the picture. There is absolutely NO! excuse for third\turd party censors. It doesn't really work on Zeronet or the OPEN! internet, BY DESIGN!!! :-)
